  <brief_title>NGAL Predictive Value of Acute Kidney Failure After Cardiac Surgery in Patients With Preoperative Chronic Kidney Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>NGAL-CKF</acronym>
  <official_title>Plasmatic Level of Neutrophil Gelatinase-Associated Lipocalin (NGAL) as a Predictive Marker of Acute Kidney Failure in Patients With Preoperative Chronic Kidney Failure Undergoing Cardiac Surgery.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
