  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary endpoint: To evaluate predictive value of plasmatic levels of Neutrophil Gelatinase
      Associated Lipocalin (NGAL) to reveal acute kidney failure after cardiac surgery in patients
      with preoperative chronic kidney failure Secondary endpoint is to obtain threshold values of
      NGAL.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
